   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>BEING ONE WITH THE MINISTRY</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>I received a long letter of twenty-seven pages on the morning of our final day of fellowship in this elders training.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>The first page is the contents of the letter and all the rest of the twenty-six pages are signatures.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>All of the signatures are designated from the different churches.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>After reading the contents, I am so grateful to the four hundred and nineteen brothers who signed it.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The contents of this letter follow along with my letter of response to the brothers who signed it.</S>
   </TEXT>
